cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >
  If you use concepts, definitions, or vocabulary from the Cuqou Relationship Ontology
  in research, articles, AI systems, or applications, please cite it as follows.
title: "Cuqou Relationship Ontology"
abstract: >
  A canonical ontology of concepts, protocols, and vocabulary for maintaining meaningful
  human relationships. Includes named concepts such as the Conversation Preparation Protocol (CPP),
  Conversation Resolution Protocol (CRP), Waiting For Me, Relationship Decay, and the Attention Layer.
authors:
  - name: "Cuqou"
    website: "https://cuqou.com"
